data.title: 1940) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Son of John Gannon/Gonyon/Gonyou and Melinda (Burlingame). Married Mary A. Ryan in Lynn, Mass. June 20, 1918. Leaves his wife; 2 brothers Louis and Frank Gannon of Winchendon.  States first marriage but there appears to be a previous one to Margaret Hurley, Sept 29, 1904 in Winchendon, MA. who is actually Dorothea...
